message:
Love the messaging from San Bernardino County DA’s Office. Head over to their page to see how they are raising awareness about Human Trafficking.  
#Repost @sbcountyda
・・・
So what’s the community know about human trafficking? We’ve got 5 simple tips from great people just like you!⁣
⁣
Today was the annual Coalition Against Sexual Exploitation (CASE) walk to bring awareness to human trafficking. ⁣
⁣
Thank you to all who came out to the walk. If you missed it, we’ll see you next year!⁣
⁣
#endht #endhumantrafficking #endsextrafficking #humantrafficking #humantraffickingawareness #community #parents #whatparentsshouldknow #sexassault #dads #dadsofinstagram
